3... Ba6 {solving the problem of developing the bishop}) (3. Rxc6 Qxe3+ 4. Kh1
4... Bb7 {offers White less}) 3... gxf6 4. Rxc6 Qxe3+ 5. Kh1 5... Bb7 {
