{How Black should not treat the Wyvill formation} 1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 Bb4
4. a3 Bxc3+ 5. bxc3 d6 6. Qc2 O-O 7. e4 e5 8. Bd3 c5 9. Ne2 Nc6 10. d5 10...
