what Nimzowitsch called a blockaded security. The only question is whether
this security is really secure} 15... Qb6 16. Bb3 c4 17. Ba4 Bc6 18. Bxc6 Qxc6
19. b3 {This is the normal way of attacking the hanging pawns} (19. Nd4) 19...
