c5 (42... g4 43. hxg4 hxg4 44. fxg4 Bxg4 45. Ng3) 43. bxc5 (43. -- 43... cxb4
44. cxb4 Rb5 45. Kb3 45... Rd4) 43... Bxc5 44. Ra4 R8d7 45. Rd1 Ba7 46. Ra3 g4
47. hxg4 hxg4 48. c4 {Mindful of the Steinitz principles Lasker makes
