Kg2 13... Bg1 $1 {In view of the threat to the e-pawn White has little choice}
14. Nxg1 (14. Rxg1 Qh2+ 15. Kf3 Qf2#) 14... Qh2+ 15. Kf3 15... e5 $3 {
